        "Uses the same-file helper e_eq_sum_prod_subsets to rewrite e n as a sum over powersetCard n univ. For each s in that sum, mem_powersetCard gives s ⊆ univ and s.card = n. Then card_le_card gives s.card ≤ Fintype.card (Fin N), so n ≤ Fintype.card (Fin N), contradicting h. The contradiction shows each summand is impossible, so the sum is zero by Finset.sum_eq_zero."
